msgid "Beacon of Light series"
msgstr "光明灯塔系列"

# Scenario description
msgid """The Beacon of Light scenario, based on the tutorial from https://daid.github.
io/EmptyEpsilon/#tabs=4.\n\nNear the far outpost of Orion-5, Exuari attacks are increasing. A diplomat \nwent missing, and your first mission is to recover him.\n\nThis scenario is limited to one player ship: the Atlantis Epsilon. Estimated \nduration: 1 hour"""
msgstr """光明灯塔场景基于教程 https://daid.github.io/EmptyEpsilon/#tabs=4。\n\n在遥远的奥瑞恩-5前哨站附近，艾苏瑞人的攻击正在加剧。一位外交官失踪了，你的第一个任务是将他营救回来。\n\n此场景仅限一艘玩家飞船：亚特兰蒂斯·伊普西隆号。预计时长：1小时"""

#: scripts/scenario_05_beacon.lua:69
msgctxt "goal-incCall"
msgid """Epsilon, please come in.\n\nWe lost contact with one of our transports, callsign RT-4, transporting the \ndiplomat named J.J. Johnson. They were heading from our research station to \nOrion-5.\n\nOur last contact with RT-4 was before it entered the nebula at sector G5. \nThe nebula is blocking our long-range scans, so we're asking you to \ninvestigate and recover RT-4 if possible."""
msgstr """伊普西隆号，请回话。\n\n我们与其中一艘运输舰——呼号RT-4——失去了联系，它正运送名为J.J.约翰逊的外交官前往奥瑞恩-5。\n\n我们最后一次与RT-4取得联系是在其进入G5扇区星云之前。星云阻挡了我们的远程扫描，因此我们请求你前去调查并尽可能找回RT-4。"""

